+subculture\"><i>Components of dress: design, manufacturing, and image-making in the fashion industry</i></a> (illustrated ed.). pp.&#160;100\u2013106. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-415-00647-3\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0-415-00647-3\">0-415-00647-3</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Assemblage+and+subculture%3A+the+Casuals+and+their+clothing&amp;rft.btitle=Components+of+dress%3A+design%2C+manufacturing%2C+and+image-making+in+the+fashion+industry&amp;rft.pages=100-106&amp;rft.edition=illustrated&amp;rft.date=1988&amp;rft.isbn=0-415-00647-3&amp;rft.au=Juliet+Ash%2C+Lee+Wright+%28chapter+author%3A+Deborah+Lloyd%29&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D03w9AAAAIAAJ%26pg%3DPA100%26lpg%3DPA100%26dq%3Dcasuals%2Bsubculture&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACasual+%28subculture%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">James Hamilton (8 May 2005). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4156/is_20050508/ai_n14619610\">\"Pundit says: 'learn to love the casuals<span style=\"padding-right:0.2em;\">'</span>\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Sunday_Herald\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Sunday Herald\">The Sunday Herald</a> 2005-05-08</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Sunday+Herald+2005-05-08&amp;rft.atitle=Pundit+says%3A+%27learn+to+love+the+casuals%27&amp;rft.date=2005-05-08&amp;rft.au=James+Hamilton&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Ffindarticles.com%2Fp%2Farticles%2Fmi_qn4156%2Fis_